%F A000340 a(n) = (3^(n+2) - 2*n - 5)/4.
%F A000340 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n+1} (n-k+1)*3^k = Sum_{k=0..n+1} k*3^(n-k+1). - _Paul Barry_, Jul 30 2004
%F A000340 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} binomial(n+2, k+2)*2^k. - _Paul Barry_, Jul 30 2004
